<br>
Parry + Arrows. Why can't we have the ability to Parry arrows. Trying to switch to shield is useless. Archers can rapid fire us down to 30% health before we even get to touch them. Hunters rapid fire + Wolf + Spear is deadly (plus they get IP too).  So either give all DW light tanks the ability to Parry arrows or hot key shield switching.<br>
